---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="About · Compleo Advisors" description={"Compleo Advisors exists to close the gap between what an organization is capable of and what the market sees. Methodology, perspective, and the team behind the work."} slug="about" pathname="/about" active="about">

<!-- ───────────────────────────  HEADER  ─────────────────────────── -->
<!-- ───────────────────────────  HERO  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner reveal">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">About Compleo Advisors</div>
      <h1>When market potential becomes <span class="accent">market position</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Compleo Advisors exists to close the gap between what an organization is capable of and what the market sees.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  EDITORIAL POSITIONING  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="editorial">
  <div class="container-reading reveal">
    <div class="editorial-prose">
      <p>
        Compleo Advisors is a rare disease strategy and creative firm. We work with rare disease biotechs,
        advocacy organizations, and pharma marketing services companies at moments of inflection: when the
        market has shifted, an asset has advanced, or the business has outgrown its current strategy. What
        you get is a partner who knows this field from the inside: sharper direction, positioning that
        differentiates, and the market movement to drive progress.
      </p>
      <p>
        What Compleo Advisors delivers is the unlock: the precise positioning and articulation of your
        differentiating value that draws the right customers, wins the right engagements, and builds a
        market position equal to your potential. Clients work with senior leadership from start to finish.
        The work doesn't stop until it is right.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  METHODOLOGY  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="methodology">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="method-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">How we work</p>
      <h2>Frame. Solve. Activate.</h2>
      <p>
        Every engagement at Compleo Advisors begins with deep organizational understanding: what drives it,
        what constrains it, what the market sees versus what is actually true, and where the real
        opportunity sits. The diagnostic shapes everything that follows.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="method-grid">
      <article class="method-card reveal">
        <svg class="corner-mark" viewBox="0 0 180 180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M 130.65,84.65 A 41,41 0 1 1 95.35,49.35" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A4A" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="118.99" cy="61.01" r="9" fill="#ED9105"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="step">Step 01</div>
        <h3>Frame.</h3>
        <p>
          Before any strategy takes shape, Compleo Advisors builds a precise understanding of this
          organization, this category, and this moment. Frame produces the diagnostic that makes everything
          that follows specific to your situation. The questions we answer here are the ones every later
          decision rests on.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="method-card reveal">
        <svg class="corner-mark" viewBox="0 0 180 180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M 130.65,84.65 A 41,41 0 1 1 95.35,49.35" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A4A" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="118.99" cy="61.01" r="9" fill="#ED9105"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="step">Step 02</div>
        <h3>Solve.</h3>
        <p>
          Strategy, positioning, and market movement built around the diagnostic. Positioning that creates a unique, ownable space in the minds of your stakeholders. Narrative that differentiates. Direction that
          holds when tested against the market.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="method-card reveal">
        <svg class="corner-mark" viewBox="0 0 180 180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M 130.65,84.65 A 41,41 0 1 1 95.35,49.35" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A4A" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="118.99" cy="61.01" r="9" fill="#ED9105"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="step">Step 03</div>
        <h3>Activate.</h3>
        <p>
          Execution that moves markets. Creative campaigns, disease education, go-to-market strategy,
          thought leadership, stakeholder partnerships, and the work in between. Senior leadership stays
          with the engagement from Frame through Activate. The work moves without a handoff.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  THREE PRACTICE AREAS  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="practice">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="practice-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Where we work</p>
      <h2>Three practice areas, one methodology.</h2>
      <p>One diagnostic-first approach, tuned to where each audience meets the market.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="practice-list">
      <article class="practice-item reveal">
        <div class="practice-number">01</div>
        <div class="practice-body">
          <h3>Catalyzing Early Commercial Potential for Rare Disease Biotech</h3>
          <p>
            Early commercial is a moment of opportunity with limited margin for error. The organizations
            that get the positioning right, that build stakeholder credibility, shape advocacy
            relationships intentionally, and translate science into a market narrative that holds, are the
            ones that attract the right partners and drive the right outcomes.
          </p>
          <p>
            Compleo Advisors grounds commercial direction in deep stakeholder insight: what advocacy
            communities, clinicians, and partners actually need to understand, believe, and act on. That
            understanding becomes positioning, messaging, and market engagement that moves with precision.
          </p>
          <a href="/for-biotech" class="arrow-link">Explore biotech engagements</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="practice-item reveal">
        <div class="practice-number">02</div>
        <div class="practice-body">
          <h3>Strengthening Rare Disease Advocacy Strategy and Communications</h3>
          <p>
            Advocacy organizations hold urgency, trust, and knowledge that no outside party can replicate.
            What many lack is the structured strategy and communications platform to translate that
            strength into external influence and durable partnerships.
          </p>
          <p>
            Compleo Advisors works with advocacy organizations to define purpose and priorities clearly,
            shape narratives that earn credibility and visibility with industry partners and critical
            stakeholders, and build the partnerships that make progress possible.
          </p>
          <a href="/for-advocacy" class="arrow-link">Explore advocacy engagements</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="practice-item reveal">
        <div class="practice-number">03</div>
        <div class="practice-body">
          <h3>Sharpening Market Position for Pharma Marketing Services Companies</h3>
          <p>
            Marketing services organizations that serve the pharmaceutical industry often face a positioning
            challenge unique to the category: expertise that can be genuinely hard to differentiate, a
            client base that is difficult to reach, and growth that depends on winning the right engagements.
          </p>
          <p>
            Compleo Advisors works with these organizations to define what actually makes them different,
            build the go-to-market approach that reaches the right buyers, and curate the thought
            leadership and market presence that builds a durable position.
          </p>
          <a href="/for-pharma-marketing-services" class="arrow-link">Explore pharma marketing services engagements</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  MEET KRISTIN  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="meet">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="meet-grid">
      <div class="headshot-column reveal">
        <div class="headshot-frame">
          <img src="/images/kristin.jpg" alt="Kristin Marvin Keller, Principal of Compleo Advisors" class="headshot-image" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        </div>
        <a class="headshot-personal-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kristinkeller/" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Connect with Kristin on LinkedIn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.5 2h-17A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2 3.5v17A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.5 22h17a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-17A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 20.5 2zM8 19H5v-9h3zM6.5 8.25A1.75 1.75 0 1 1 8.3 6.5a1.78 1.78 0 0 1-1.8 1.75zM19 19h-3v-4.74c0-1.42-.6-1.93-1.38-1.93A1.74 1.74 0 0 0 13 14.19a.66.66 0 0 0 0 .14V19h-3v-9h2.9v1.3a3.11 3.11 0 0 1 2.7-1.4c1.55 0 3.36.86 3.36 3.66z"/></svg>
          <span>Connect with Kristin on LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="meet-copy reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Meet the founder</p>
        <h2>Kristin Marvin Keller, Principal.</h2>
        <p>
          Kristin brings 25+ years of pharmaceutical and rare disease marketing experience, with 20 spent
          also as an organizational leader driving B2B strategy and execution in professional service
          environments. She began her career in digital agencies, then built her own rare disease patient
          marketing agency, where she built her operational instincts, strategic savvy, client partnership
          skills, and business development discipline.
        </p>
        <p>
          Across agency and client-side leadership roles as a co-founder, managing director, chief
          strategy officer, and chief commercial officer, she has consistently delivered with strategic
          clarity and commercial accountability. Kristin is both an executive leader and an entrepreneur,
          with a track record of building and transforming organizations.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through Compleo Advisors, she works with life sciences companies at growth inflection points:
          helping leadership teams get clear on where they are going, sharpen how they compete, and build
          the commercial capability needed to scale.
        </p>

        <div class="meet-meta">
          <div>
            <strong>Based in</strong>
            Boston, MA
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Connect</strong>
            <a href="#">LinkedIn →</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Email</strong>
            <a href="mailto:kristin@compleoadvisors.com">kristin@compleoadvisors.com</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  TEAM MODEL  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="team">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="team-inner reveal">
      <h2>The right team, assembled for the engagement.</h2>
      <p>
        Compleo Advisors operates as a senior-led firm with a network of specialist partners across rare
        disease strategy, creative, advocacy engagement, and activation. Every engagement is led by senior
        leadership and staffed with the right specialists for the work, without the overhead of a layered
        agency structure. Every engagement gets the team it needs, built for the work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  CLOSING CTA  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="closing reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>If you are at a moment of inflection, we would welcome a conversation.</h2>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      <a href="/insights" class="btn btn-secondary">See our latest thinking <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  FOOTER  ─────────────────────────── -->

</SiteLayout>

<style is:global>
/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   COMPLEO ADVISORS — ABOUT MOCKUP v1
   Phase 2 of website redesign · Single-file HTML
   Design system inherited from Phase 1 homepage v2
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */

/* tokens in global.css */

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  font-size: var(--fs-body);
  line-height: var(--lh-body);
  color: var(--c-body);
  background: var(--c-white);
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
}
img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
a { color: var(--c-charcoal); text-decoration: none; transition: color .15s ease; }
a:hover { color: var(--c-amber); }

h1, h2, h3, h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: var(--lh-tight);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
h1 { font-size: var(--fs-h1-desktop); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h2-desktop); font-weight: 600; }
h3 { font-size: var(--fs-h3-desktop); font-weight: 500; line-height: var(--lh-snug); }

p { margin: 0 0 1em; }
p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: var(--content-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}
.container-narrow {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: var(--content-narrow);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}
.container-reading {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: var(--content-reading);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}

section { padding: var(--section-y-desktop) 0; }

.eyebrow {
  font-size: var(--fs-small);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 14px 26px;
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .18s ease, color .18s ease, border-color .18s ease, transform .18s ease;
}
.btn-primary { background: var(--c-amber); color: var(--c-white); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--c-charcoal); color: var(--c-white); }
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--c-rule-gray);
}
.btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--c-charcoal); color: var(--c-near-black); }
.btn .arrow { display: inline-block; transition: transform .18s ease; }
.btn:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

.arrow-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.arrow-link::after { content: "→"; transition: transform .18s ease; }
.arrow-link:hover { color: var(--c-amber); }
.arrow-link:hover::after { transform: translateX(4px); }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   HEADER / NAV (inherited)
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.site-header {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
  backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(10px);
  border-bottom: var(--rule);
}
.nav {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 18px 0;
}
.brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--c-near-black); }
.brand-mark { width: 36px; height: 36px; }
.brand-words { display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1; }
.brand-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  letter-spacing: -0.005em;
}
.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 28px;
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
}
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.nav-links a.active { color: var(--c-amber); }
.nav-cta {
  margin-left: 10px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background: var(--c-amber);
  color: var(--c-white) !important;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--c-charcoal); color: var(--c-white) !important; }
.nav-toggle {
  display: none;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  font-size: 22px;
  padding: 8px;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   HERO (wide editorial)
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  padding: 84px 0 18px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-inner { max-width: 1080px; }
.hero-eyebrow {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  margin-bottom: 44px;
}
.hero-eyebrow::before {
  content: "";
  display: inline-block;
  width: 48px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--c-amber);
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(44px, 7.2vw, 88px);
  line-height: 1.04;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  max-width: 20ch;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}
.hero h1 .accent {
  color: var(--c-amber);
  background-image: linear-gradient(var(--c-amber), var(--c-amber));
  background-size: 100% 6px;
  background-position: 0 96%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  padding-bottom: 2px;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(20px, 2.1vw, 24px);
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  max-width: 56ch;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   EDITORIAL POSITIONING BLOCK
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.editorial { padding: 32px 0 var(--section-y-desktop); }
.editorial-prose p {
  font-size: 19px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.editorial-prose p:first-child::first-letter {
  font-size: 56px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  float: left;
  line-height: 0.95;
  margin: 6px 12px 0 0;
}
.editorial-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   METHODOLOGY (Frame · Solve · Activate)
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.methodology { background: var(--c-light-gray); }
.method-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
}
.method-header .eyebrow { text-align: center; }
.method-header h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }
.method-header p {
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.method-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}
.method-card {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--c-warm-cream);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 40px 32px 36px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(237, 145, 5, 0.18);
  transition: transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
}
.method-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 16px 32px -18px rgba(74, 74, 74, 0.22);
}
.method-card .corner-mark {
  position: absolute;
  top: 20px;
  right: 20px;
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  opacity: 0.55;
}
.method-card .step {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.method-card h3 {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.method-card p {
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   THREE PRACTICE AREAS STACK
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.practice {
  padding-top: calc(var(--section-y-desktop) + 12px);
  padding-bottom: calc(var(--section-y-desktop) + 12px);
}
.practice-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 44px;
}
.practice-header h2 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.practice-header p {
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  font-size: 17px;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.practice-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 40px;
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.practice-item {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
  gap: 32px;
  padding-bottom: 40px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-rule-gray);
}
.practice-item:last-child {
  padding-bottom: 0;
  border-bottom: none;
}
.practice-number {
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  padding-top: 6px;
}
.practice-body h3 {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.practice-body p {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.practice-body .arrow-link { margin-top: 4px; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   MEET KRISTIN
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.meet { background: var(--c-warm-cream); }
.meet-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
  gap: 56px;
  align-items: start;
}
.headshot-frame {
  position: relative;
  aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
  background: var(--c-white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  border: 1px solid var(--c-rule-gray);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 42px -22px rgba(74, 74, 74, 0.28);
}
.headshot-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center top;
  display: block;
}
.meet-copy .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 14px; }
.meet-copy h2 {
  font-size: clamp(30px, 3.4vw, 40px);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.meet-copy p {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.meet-meta {
  margin-top: 28px;
  padding-top: 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 74, 74, 0.18);
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 24px 36px;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.meet-meta strong {
  display: block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.meet-meta a { color: var(--c-amber); font-weight: 500; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   TEAM MODEL
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.team { padding: var(--section-y-desktop) 0; }
.team-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  gap: 64px;
  max-width: 1080px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.team-inner h2 {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  line-height: 1.25;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--c-amber);
  padding-left: 20px;
}
.team-inner p {
  font-size: 18px;
